Future features.

 1. Possibly DataUtility module that simplifies making the data for
    RangeArea and RangeBar?
 2. Ability to change the mark
    a. Size
    b. Style (cross vs. dot, ellipse vs. dot, dot vs. line, etc.)
 3. RangeBar/RangeArea: Other mark types
    a. lowest high
    b. highest low
    c. largest variation
    d. smallest variation
 4. Whisker: other mark types
    a. All low ticks
    b. All high ticks
 5. Display a reference line on sparkline
    a. Particular x value
    b. Particular y value
 6. Band of y-values feature
    - See the ET article
 7. x/y args for Line and Area?
 8. Ability to set baseline
 9. Axes?
10. Labels?
11. Opacity features.
12. Combining multiple data sets in one sparkline.
    a. Overlapping
    b. One above the others
